## 0.3.0 — USN Journal Support (code-complete; NOT yet published to NuGet)

Code-complete. Three APIs:
- `MftVolume.QueryUsnJournal()` — get current journal cursor
- `MftVolume.ReadUsnJournal(cursor)` — batch catch-up read
- `MftVolume.WatchUsnJournal(cursor, cancellationToken)` — live IAsyncEnumerable event stream
- `FileAttributes` sourced from `$STANDARD_INFORMATION` (preferred) with `$FILE_NAME` fallback
- **[ADDED 2026-07-06]** VolumeBroker subsystem (extracted from file-wizard, branch
  `feat/volume-broker`): JournalBrokerHost/Client, BrokerProtocol, ScanPayload/ScanRecord,
  ElevatedEntryPoint `--broker` + BrokerLauncher, BrokerDiagnostics — single-UAC elevated
  scanning + live USN watch for non-elevated consumers. Consumers wired: file-wizard
  (submodule pin) and git-wizard (`--watch`, vendored DLLs).

